                  <scopecontent>
                     <p>Autograph draft, of ll. 57-144, here untitled, following a
									<extref href="http://www.thomasgray.org/cgi-bin/display.cgi?text=tgal0236"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">letter</extref>
								to <extref href="http://www.thomasgray.org/resources/glnames.shtml#Wharton, Thomas, 1717-1794"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <persname normal="Wharton, Thomas, 1717-1794">Thomas
										Wharton</persname>
                        </extref>, <date normal="17550821" era="ce" calendar="gregorian">21 August 
											1755</date>, but according to <bibref title="http://www.thomasgray.org/resources/bibll.shtml#T/W_1971"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <title render="italic" linktype="simple">Correspondence of Thomas Gray</title> (1971),
									vol. i,  434</bibref> very probably written at the beginning
								of <extref href="http://www.thomasgray.org/resources/table.shtml#1757"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <date normal="175706" era="ce" calendar="gregorian">June 1757</date>
                        </extref>.</p>
